events.name: EV001エマ盗賊団包囲網1-11自動実行

parameters:
Imperial Secret Service Member: 'We are receiving corpses
one after another from the Camps region.'

Court Magician Eratoma: Oh my, how wonderful! The thickness
of the bones in the thief's corpse is truly remarkable!
Court Magician Eratoma: Will you also come and take a look?

Imperial Secret Service Member: I'll pass, but do we really
need this many corpses?

Court Magician Eratoma: Of course! Including the selection
process, I want even more corpses.
Court Magician Eratoma: I will show you a real monster.

Court Magician Eratoma: Even if I were to become a monster
myself
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
